      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers straightforward value for anyone seeking inexpensive transportation or a practical project. It shows its age cosmetically and mechanically, but it remains an accessible option for buyers who want a low-entry-price vehicle with potential. A smart buy for the right owner who appreciates honest value.",
