    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest budget-friendly car that starts, runs, and gets the job done. It\u2019s definitely not a showpiece, but if you need affordable wheels, a simple runabout, or a project with potential, this could be a great fit. Priced fairly for what it is, and I\u2019d rather be upfront and easy to deal with than oversell it. Come take a look and see if it suits your needs.",
