      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong-running driver with solid bones and plenty of mechanical character. The engine pulls cleanly, transmission engages as it should, and the chassis feels composed enough to enjoy as-is while you sort the cosmetic and age-related needs. Not a show car, but a straightforward, usable project with good fundamentals for someone who appreciates an honest car with real potential. Priced to move for the condition.",
