      "description": "A gritty diamond-in-the-rough with undeniable character, this car has the kind of presence that turns a simple drive into a story. The body lines still carry timeless appeal, and for the right buyer it offers a fantastic canvas for a budget-friendly runabout, weekend tinkering project, or creative restoration journey. If you appreciate machines with soul and see opportunity where others see ordinary, this one is ready for its next chapter.",
